Fremennik sea boots is a reward from completing parts of the Fremennik Diary. There are four types, depending on which part of the diary the player has completed. Those are:

  • Fremennik sea boots 1, from the easy tasks set
  • Fremennik sea boots 2, from the medium tasks set
  • Fremennik sea boots 3, from the hard tasks set
  • Fremennik sea boots 4, from the elite tasks set

'''Fremennik sea boots''' is a reward from completing parts of the [[Fremennik Diary]]. There are four types, depending on which part of the diary the player has completed. Those are:

*[[Fremennik sea boots 1]], from the easy tasks set
*[[Fremennik sea boots 2]], from the medium tasks set
*[[Fremennik sea boots 3]], from the hard tasks set
*[[Fremennik sea boots 4]], from the elite tasks set
